{"TopicId":202734,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Max Speed Challenge.","CreatedByName":"determinationmaster","CreatedById":209947,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-28T15:30:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"determinationmaster","CreatedById":209947,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-28T15:30:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthis challenge is simple: get to the fastest speed you can while in kerbin\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E.\u00A0 use any means neccessary. the rules:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. no cheats. just dont open the cheat menu. exploits and glitches ok.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. only stock. no part mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nleaderboard will be posted here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst Place:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSecond Place:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThird Place:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-05-28T15:31:26Z\u0022 title=\u002205/28/2021 03:31  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EMay 28, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by determinationmaster\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rakete","CreatedById":208801,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-28T16:40:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow is the maximum speed recorded? Is the maximum speed the speed\u00A0when leaving kerbins \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E after a long acceleration? e.g. after a long ion / nerva accerleration? As only Kerbins \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E is the limit, isn\u0027t this a \u0022who gets the most \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0022-contest, as leaving kerbins \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E takes a while, so that \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Thrust-to-weight ratio\u0022\u003ETWR\u003C/abbr\u003E isn\u0027t the real issue?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"determinationmaster","CreatedById":209947,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-30T23:14:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsorry i wasnt clear, your score is the maximum orbital speed you achieve while still in kerbin\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003Esoi\u003C/abbr\u003E. i chose kerbin because if you exit kerbin you start off at\u00A0 10000 m/s.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-31T02:31:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre we allowed to leave Kerbin\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E and re-enter it later?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jinnantonix","CreatedById":188889,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-31T05:59:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMax orbital speed = 4.425 km/s\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022150\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/RyQLTTWypWc?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jinnantonix","CreatedById":188889,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-31T10:58:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo top speed must be within Kerbin \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E.\u00A0 Is there any constraint on the craft after reaching top speed?\u00A0 For example can the craft fly back out of the Kerbin \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E?\u00A0 Does the craft have to be able to land on Kerbin again?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xendelaar","CreatedById":139535,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-03T11:23:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell... I don\u0027t know if this count as an entry , because I only have a video containing the highlights of the mission, but I once burnt up 18km/s of delta v\u00A0 in order to get to Duna pretty fast... I believe the burn was completed inside the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E of Kerbin, but that isn\u0027t really shown in the video..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEither way, it\u0027s nice challenge \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0and here is a small video of my \u0027speedrun to Duna\u0027.. (btw..my apologies\u00A0for the tik tok-ish music)\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/IGTnrMHPLcM?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}